    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan. Validation evidence demonstrates RH index prediction error of 6.8% mean absolute percentage error across five operating points, with all predictions within experimental 95% confidence intervals. GCI of 1.3% confirms adequate mesh resolution. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device, and the relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
